item-1.paragraph-1: This Privacy Policy describes how Yudaneru collects, uses, and discloses information associated with an identified or identifiable individual (referred to in this Privacy Policy as “Personal Data”) and what choices you have around this activity. item-1.paragraph-2: When we refer to “Yudaneru”, we mean Yudaneru Technologies, LLC or Yudaneru Technologies Limited, as explained in more detail in the “Identifying the Data Controller and Processor” section below.
